Day 1 (December 22)
We’re excited to launch the “Har Ghar Ped Lagayega” campaign, a fundraising initiative aimed at planting 10,000 trees in Dehradun. This project is part of our larger “Reviving Doon Valley” initiative, set to commence in July 2025.

Huge thanks to Milli Thawani, owner of Cloud 9 Salon, for partnering with us. Your trust and support mean everything. @milli_0604 @cloud9salon 

Objective:
Plant 10,000 trees in Dehradun
Revitalize the Doon Valley ecosystem
Promote environmental sustainability

How You Can Help:
Donate to support tree planting
Spread awareness about the campaign
Join us as a volunteer in 2025

Together, let’s make a difference and revive the Doon Valley.

latestPosts.caption:
Join us as we dive into the creative process behind our latest video for Kamni Sarees. Our journey begins with an intricate photoshoot, where each saree is meticulously styled to highlight its unique fabric and design. Our team works diligently to capture the essence of Kamni Sarees through carefully planned shots and lighting. 

Once the footage is in, we transition to the editing suite, where we weave together each frame with precision. Every color, texture, and movement is enhanced to ensure the final video reflects the rich heritage and contemporary elegance of Kamni Sarees. 

This video is more than just a showcase; it’s a celebration of craftsmanship and style. Stay tuned to see how we bring the timeless allure of Kamni Sarees to life, from concept to final cut.
